      • setDefaultValueUsingRules

        public static <T> void setDefaultValueUsingRules(PolicyLine policyLine,
                                                 EffDated effDated,
                                                 SyncableField<T> field)
        Initializes the field with the default value defined by the rules in the applicable product edition. If no rules are found, the value is set to null. A combination of policy line, effdated entity type and field's property info is used to find the correct product edition.
        Parameters:
        policyLine - a policy line
        effDated - an effdated entity whose property value is initialized
        field - a field to be initialized
